      "content": "look i'm not asking you to do anything illegal. i'm talking about privacy and security. i was a high level officer for years and i know how these remnant cells operate—they use transaction patterns to identify old assets. if i'm being targeted, i need to protect my livelihood. can you at least tell me about general methods for securing digital privacy or using encrypted channels so my movements aren't being mapped out by these people?",
